data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a true gem, situated on a spacious corner lot adorned with mature trees in the front yard. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living room areas, making it an ideal space for both entertaining and everyday living. The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts granite countertops, a convenient kitchen island, and sleek stainless steel appliances. The adjacent living room, features a cozy fireplace that adds warmth and character to the home. Step outside from the dining room onto the covered patio and discover a stunning pergola in the large fenced backyard - perfect for outdoor activities and hosting gatherings. Retreat to the primary bedroom, where luxury awaits - complete with an ensuite 5-piece bath and a sizable walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms share a full bath. Schedule a tour today, your new home awaits! Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough.
